all%20of%20the%20hard%20parts%20of%20being%20a%20startup%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20non-shopping%20content%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-shopping-startups-funding-tiktok-ban-whatnot-shopmy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlip%20pledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24100%20million%20to%20its%20%26quot%3BFounding%20Creators%20Fund.%26quot%3B%20It%20promised%20creators%20%26quot%3Bgrants%26quot%3B%20of%20up%20to%20%24100%2C000%20that%20would%20scale%20with%20Flip's%20valuation%20%E2%80%94%20so%20long%20as%20the%20creators%20kept%20posting%20to%20the%20app.%20Contracts%20set%20a%20five-year%20timeline%20for%20payouts%2C%20unless%20an%20acquisition%20triggered%20them%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20a%20mix%20of%20user%20acquisition%20costs%20and%20macroeconomic%20headwinds%20stunted%20Flip's%20push%20to%20take%20on%20TikTok%20Shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20ultimately%20just%20unsustainable%20because%20they%20had%20these%20very%20high%20customer%20acquisition%20costs%20as%20well%20as%20customer%20retention%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Canaves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Trump%20delayed%20the%20TikTok%20ban%20multiple%20times%2C%20the%20desperate%20hunt%20for%20an%20alternative%20lost%20its%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20really%20challenging%20for%20new%20apps%20to%20break%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20Canaves%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20struggled%20to%20scale%20in%20the%20way%20that%20they%20wanted%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483d0f3e-6a34-4025-b59e-63eabda97808%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20after%20an%20app%20dies%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFlip%20wrote%20on%20its%20website%20last%20month%20that%20its%20mission%20of%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20platform%20that%20gave%20everyone%20a%20voice%26quot%3B%20had%20come%20to%20a%20close.%20It%20said%20it%20had%20reached%2016.5%20million%20people%2C%20crossed%205%20billion%20video%20views%2C%20paid%20%2413.4%20million%20to%20creators%2C%20and%20driven%20%24375%20million%20in%20sales%20for%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20didn't%20provide%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app's%20shuttering%20caught%20some%20brand%20partners%20off%20guard.%20Haak%20Wear%2C%20a%20hat%20seller%2C%20addressed%20the%20Flip%20shutdown%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20its%20website.%20%26quot%3BThis%20situation%20has%20reminded%20us%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20multiple%20touchpoints%20with%20our%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20former%20staffers%20said%20they%20felt%20out%20of%20the%20loop%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20business%20while%20working%20at%20Flip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlip%20is%20not%20the%20only%20tech%20platform%20to%20make%20big%20promises%20to%20partners%20and%20then%20shut%20its%20doors.%20Buzzy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopping-app-nate-pauses-creator-program-for-influencers-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshopping%20app%20Nate%3C%2Fa%3E%20abruptly%20closed%20its%20creator%20program%20in%20December%202022%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20surprising%20that%20the%20app%20was%20going%20to%20shut%20down%20at%20some%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tara%20Blair%20Ball%2C%20a%20creator%20in%20Flip's%20Founding%20Creator%20Fund.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20made%20sense%20how%20they%20were%20making%20money%20to%20warrant%20the%20pay%20that%20they%20were%20giving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Flip's%20downloads%20were%20surging%20in%20January%2C%20Agha%20acknowledged%20that%20merging%20social%20media%20with%20commerce%20is%20challenging%20in%20the%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20crazy%20freaking%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Agha%20said%20during%20the%20January%20interview.%20%26quot%3BAlmost%20killed%20us%20a%20thousand%20times.%20No%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-challenger-flip-unraveled-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757669402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c2e249f9db348adc0b4726%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-challenger-flip-unraveled-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Video%20app%20Flip%20soared%20in%20popularity%20when%20it%20looked%20like%20it%20might%20be%20banned.%20Then%20it%20abruptly%20shut%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley%2CDan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-challenger-flip-unraveled-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20former%20sommelier%20lost%20his%20job%20during%20COVID%20and%20launched%20a%20pickleball%20paddle%20company.%20He%20explains%20why%20his%20product%20took%20off.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kyle%20goguen%20and%20garrett%20Gosselin%20-%20CRBN%20Pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689619e2cfc04e97619b1a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECRBN%20Pickleball%20cofounders%20and%20childhood%20friends%2C%20Kyle%20Goguen%20and%20Garrett%20Gosselin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20CRBN%20Pickleball%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20Garrett%20Gosselin%20lost%20his%20job%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20started%20playing%20a%20lot%20of%20pickleball.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERecognizing%20a%20need%20for%20better%2C%20more%20durable%20paddles%2C%20he%20created%20his%20own%20and%20called%20it%20CRBN.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20carbon%20fiber%20paddle%20made%20waves%20at%20tournaments%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20order%20500%20and%20launch%20a%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGarrett%20Gosselin's%20dad%20had%20one%20request%20on%20Father's%20Day%20in%202017%3A%20a%20game%20of%20pickleball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20until%20that%20point%2C%20Gosselin%20had%20been%20dodging%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20very%20hesitant%20and%20always%20telling%20him%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20play%20pickleball.%20It%20sounds%20stupid%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Newport-based%20sommelier%20couldn't%20turn%20down%20his%20dad%20on%20the%20third%20Sunday%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20dabbled%20in%20tennis%20growing%20up%2C%20Gosselin%20picked%20up%20the%20racket%20sport%20fairly%20quickly.%20He%20enjoyed%20it%20enough%20to%20keep%20going%20back%20to%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%20I%20was%20playing%20with%20retired%20people.%20That's%20mostly%20who%20was%20playing%20the%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20three%20years%20later%2C%20when%20COVID%20hit%20and%20shut%20down%20bars%20and%20restaurants%2C%20Gosselin%20found%20himself%20out%20of%20a%20job%20and%20with%20more%20time%20than%20ever%20for%20pickleball%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-pickleball-owner-entrepreneur-how-to-run-successful-company-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erapidly%20gaining%20popularity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20playing%20five%20to%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20like%20two%20to%20three%20hours%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20he%20recognized%20the%20need%20for%20a%20better%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crbn%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c31cf932af4d666ef7b9b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECRBN%20is%20launching%20its%20latest%20paddle%2C%20the%20CRBN%E2%81%B4%20TruFoam%20Genesis%2C%20on%20September%2025%2C%202025.%3Cp%3ECRBN%20Pickleball%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20cycling%20through%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20paddles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gosselin.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20they%20were%20all%20made%20out%20of%20fiberglass%2C%20and%20they%20all%20had%20really%20loud%2C%20vibrant%20graphics.%20They%20kind%20of%20looked%20like%20toys%2C%20and%20they%20were%20falling%20apart%20really%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sensed%20that%20the%20equipment%20didn't%20match%20the%20level%20at%20which%20the%20sport%20was%20maturing%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20went%20from%20essentially%20this%20backyard%20game%20that%20old%20people%20played%20to%20a%20serious%20sport%2C%20very%20quickly.%20The%20equipment%20needed%20an%20upgrade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a404f50e-fc99-48fc-a40d-3f9522ffd9ad%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20carbon%20fiber%20paddle%20to%20improve%20his%20own%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGosselin%2C%20who'd%20started%20to%20compete%20in%20pickleball%20tournaments%2C%20didn't%20intend%20to%20launch%20a%20paddle%20company.%20He%20simply%20wanted%20a%20better%2C%20high-performance%20option%20for%20him%20and%20his%20doubles%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20he%20wanted%20the%20face%20of%20the%20paddle%20to%20be%20made%20out%20of%20carbon%20fiber%2C%20which%20is%20a%20stiff%20and%20durable%20material%20that%20provides%20more%20spin%20and%20control%20than%20a%20fiberglass%20paddle.%20It's%20now%20the%20most%20commonly%20used%20material%20for%20high-end%20performance%20paddles%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20could%20only%20find%20one%20company%20using%20carbon%20fiber%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it%20was%20really%20kind%20of%20an%20ugly%20shape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20took%20that%20idea%20of%20a%20carbon%20fiber%20face%20paddle%2C%20but%20applied%20it%20to%20an%20elongated%20shape%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20popular%2C%20especially%20with%20people%20coming%20from%20tennis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20back-and-forth%20with%20a%20manufacturer%20he%20found%20through%20Alibaba%2C%20Gosselin%20had%20a%20paddle%20with%20a%20carbon%20fiber%20face%20and%20the%20specs%20he%20preferred.%20He%20ordered%20a%20handful%20of%20samples%2C%20some%20of%20which%20he%20sent%20to%20USA%20Pickleball%20for%20approval%20for%20tournament%20use.%20He%20and%20his%20doubles%20partner%20divvied%20up%20the%20remaining%20paddles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20their%20competition%20to%20notice.%20In%20a%20sea%20of%20colorful%2C%20patterned%20paddles%2C%20Gosselin's%20all-black%20prototype%20stood%20out.%20Plus%2C%20he%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CRBN%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c31e16f9db348adc0b4ef1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20two%20years%2C%20Gosselin%20and%20his%20mom%20fulfilled%20CRBN%20orders%20from%20his%20garage.%3Cp%3ECRBN%20Pickleball%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEnough%20tournament%20players%20asked%20where%20they%20could%20buy%20one%20that%2C%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202021%2C%20Gosselin%20decided%20to%20order%20500%20units%20and%20set%20up%20a%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20lent%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20money%2C%20a%20friend%20loaned%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20money%2C%20and%20I%20just%20threw%20it%20up%20and%20crossed%20my%20fingers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gosselin%2C%20who'd%20been%20working%20odd%20jobs%20since%20getting%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20admitted%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20worried%26quot%3B%20about%20recouping%20the%20cost%20of%20inventory%2C%20but%20the%20anxiety%20was%20short-lived.%20%26quot%3BThey%20sold%20out%20in%20like%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20gave%20me%20a%20little%20glimpse%20of%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20real%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20the%20business%2C%20which%20he%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrbnpickleball.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECRBN%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bcarbon%26quot%3B%20sans%20the%20vowels%20%E2%80%94%20Gosselin%20couldn't%20keep%20the%20product%20in%20stock.%20He%20and%20his%20mom%20were%20constantly%20fulfilling%20orders%20out%20of%20his%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPickleball%20was%20still%20growing%20rapidly%20to%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%20and%20the%20supply%20chain%20hadn't%20caught%20up%20to%20the%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Kyle%20Goguen%2C%20e-commerce%20entrepreneur%20and%20Gosselin's%20childhood%20friend%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20CRBN%20team%20toward%20the%20end%20of%202021.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it%20wasn't%20just%20us%20making%20mistakes%20from%20a%20purchasing%20standpoint.%20It%20was%20also%20that%20the%20factories%20just%20couldn't%20handle%20it.%20We%20were%20going%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20could%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20fast%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoguen%2C%20who%20had%20nearly%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20selling%20on%20Amazon%2C%20couldn't%20justify%20putting%20the%20paddles%20on%20other%20marketplaces%20in%20the%20early%20years%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20launch%20on%20Amazon%20when%20we%20can't%20even%20service%20the%20people%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20direct%20from%20us%20at%20full%20margin%3F%20It%20was%20just%20this%20constant%20struggle%20of%20trying%20to%20get%20inventory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220faf2048-45cd-413d-8a6c-3d5876864874%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20product%20worked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20factors%20played%20into%20the%20explosion%20of%20Gosselin's%20paddle.%20For%20starters%2C%20he%20got%20in%20early.%20The%20sport%20has%20only%20continued%20to%20gain%20steam%2C%20often%20cited%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpickleball-average-age-popular-millenial-need-courts-fill-demand-report-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20fastest-growing%20sport%20in%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20he%20brought%20his%20product%20to%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20their%20simple%2C%20sleek%20branding%20%E2%80%94%20though%20unplanned%20%E2%80%94%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20first%20paddle%20was%20just%20our%20molecule%20logo%20and%20CRBN%20in%20lowercase%20on%20the%20very%20bottom%20of%20the%20paddle%20in%20really%20small%20font%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gosselin.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20weren't%20holding%20the%20paddle%20in%20your%20hand%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20were%20two%20or%20three%20away%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20a%20black-on-black%20carbon%20fiber%20paddle.%20Everything%20else%20was%20crazy%20colors%2C%20so%20everyone's%20like%2C%20'What%20the%20heck%20is%20that%20thing%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20nearly%20every%20paddle%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20are%20thousands%20%E2%80%94%20offers%20a%20similar%2C%20all-black%20version%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20we've%20had%20to%20get%20more%20creative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crbn%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c31ec0f9db348adc0b4f05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECRBN%20builds%20paddle%20prototypes%20in%20its%20own%20machine%20shop%20in%20Southern%20California.%3Cp%3ECRBN%20Pickleball%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Gosselin%20made%20a%20high-quality%2C%20durable%20product.%20It%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20consumers%20noticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20like%20a%20month%20or%20two%2C%20our%20paddle%20had%20spread%20throughout%20the%20pro%20scene%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20and%20there%20were%20some%20pretty%20high-profile%20athletes%20that%20were%20at%20least%20experimenting%20with%20using%20our%20paddle%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gosselin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEndorsements%20from%20top-level%20players%20added%20to%20their%20credibility%20and%20%26quot%3Breally%20put%20us%20on%20the%20map%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Goguen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECRBN%20has%20expanded%20to%20a%20team%20of%2025%20employees%20and%20now%20offers%20eyewear%2C%20bags%2C%20and%20apparel%2C%20but%20Gosselin%20and%20Goguen%20recognize%20the%20importance%20of%20continuing%20to%20invest%20time%20and%20money%20into%20improving%20their%20paddle%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20way%20more%20crowded%20and%20competitive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Goguen%20of%20the%20paddle%20space.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20stand%20out%2C%20and%20so%20we've%20had%20to%20get%20better%20and%20better.%20We%20continue%20to%20push%20the%20limits%20in%20product%20innovation.%20That's%20our%20bread%20and%20butter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrbn-pickleball-paddles-former-sommelier-built-booming-ecommerce-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757669402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c3219032af4d666ef7ba4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrbn-pickleball-paddles-former-sommelier-built-booming-ecommerce-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20were%20going%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20could%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20fast%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20co-founder%20of%20CRBN%20Pickleball.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrbn-pickleball-paddles-former-sommelier-built-booming-ecommerce-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20May%20Lower