it%20out.%20I%20had%20spent%20years%20helping%20small%20business%20clients%20with%20lending%20and%20commercial%20strategy.%20I%20understood%20balance%20sheets%2C%20profit%20and%20loss%20statements%2C%20and%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20business.%20Coffee%2C%20I%20figured%2C%20could%20be%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20found%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-coffee-is-more-expensive-roasters-cafe-owners-prices-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20roaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20willing%20to%20train%20me%20like%20a%20new%20employee%2C%20practicing%20for%20six%20months%20by%20making%20drinks%20for%20my%20dad's%20work%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20September%202019%2C%20we%20opened%20our%20stand%2C%20and%20a%20few%20months%20later%20expanded%20into%20food%20carts%2C%20a%20beer%20trailer%2C%20and%20even%20a%20small%20outdoor%20concert%20space.%20It%20was%20more%20than%20coffee%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20build%20community%20in%20a%20town%20that%20didn't%20have%20much%20of%20a%20gathering%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ac0819f-1f91-4039-a498-49aa0145da7d%5C%22%3EStruggling%20to%20stay%20open%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20all%20that%20work%2C%20by%20early%202023%2C%20the%20coffee%20side%20of%20the%20business%20was%20struggling.%20Some%20days%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20it%20made%20more%20sense%20to%20close%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20bar%2C%20which%20was%20doing%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20posting%20casually%20on%20TikTok%20since%202021%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20fancy%2C%20just%20drink-making%20videos%20and%20lighthearted%20content.%20But%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20I%20stumbled%20on%20a%20quirky%20product%20online%3A%20oversize%2034-ounce%20plastic%20buckets%20with%20handles%20and%20straws.%20They%20reminded%20me%20of%20fairground%20lemonade%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%2015%20and%20filmed%20a%20quick%20video%20of%20myself%20making%20a%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-coffee-chain-has-the-best-black-coffee-on-ice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eiced%20Americano%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20one.%20It%20wasn't%20my%20best%20content%2C%20but%20the%20internet%20thought%20otherwise.%20The%20clip%20went%20viral%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20customers%20were%20lined%20up%2015%20to%2020%20cars%20deep%2C%20spilling%20onto%20the%20highway.%20I%20had%20only%20one%20barista%20scheduled.%20I%20called%20my%20boyfriend%20to%20rush%20in%20and%20help%2C%20even%20though%20he'd%20never%20worked%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-espresso-machines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eespresso%20machine.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20were%20completely%20overwhelmed%2C%20but%20the%20excitement%20was%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d0e510a-f92d-45ca-a93e-c8b7107fff58%5C%22%3EGoing%20viral%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20one%2062-second%20video%20doubled%2C%20then%20tripled%20our%20sales.%20In%20the%20months%20since%2C%20we've%20hired%20two%20more%20employees%2C%20extended%20our%20hours%2C%20and%20started%20selling%20%26quot%3Bbucket%20refills%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20%241%20discount%20for%20customers%20who%20bring%20them%20back%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sustainable%20perk%20that%20has%20built%20loyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20drive%20hours%20to%20visit.%20One%20family%20comes%20every%20Sunday%20from%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20away.%20Others%20have%20traveled%20from%20Idaho%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20beyond%20just%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Bthe%20viral%20bucket%20shop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attention%20has%20been%20surreal.%20Local%20media%20covered%20us%2C%20and%20we've%20had%20partnerships%20with%20larger%20food%20companies.%20Strangers%20stop%20me%20in%20town%20to%20say%20they%20recognize%20me%20from%20TikTok.%20It's%20strange%20to%20be%20called%20%26quot%3Bfamous%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20just%20had%20a%20silly%20idea%20that%20resonated%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223082d32d-1f0a-4167-8544-35a60063bb2e%5C%22%3EFrom%20corporate%20banker%20to%20community%20builder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20most%20rewarding%20isn't%20just%20the%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20way%20our%20little%20business%20has%20energized%20the%20town.%20Damascus%20never%20had%20a%20space%20for%20concerts%2C%20vendor%20fairs%2C%20or%20car%20shows%20before.%20Now%2C%20our%20lot%20hosts%20all%20of%20those%2C%20with%20the%20coffee%20stand%20at%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skills%20I%20learned%20in%20banking%20helped%20me%20run%20the%20numbers%2C%20train%20my%20staff%2C%20and%20set%20up%20systems.%20But%20what%20I%20didn't%20expect%20was%20how%20fulfilling%20it%20would%20be%20to%20create%20something%20joyful%20in%20my%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20was%20leaving%20behind%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flost-2-jobs-by-25-no-job-secure-make-stability-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecure%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20gamble.%20And%20for%20a%20while%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20that%20gamble%20might%20not%20pay%20off.%20Then%20TikTok%20turned%20it%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20instead%20of%20debating%20whether%20to%20close%20the%20stand%2C%20I'm%20asking%20myself%20how%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand.%20They're%20far%20better%20problems%20to%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20trade%20them%20for%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-corporate-banking-career-open-coffee-shop-viral-tiktok-marketing-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757668261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c3525332af4d666ef7bed9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-corporate-banking-career-open-coffee-shop-viral-tiktok-marketi