cfo-warns-software-disruption-saas-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESarah%20Friar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20at%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20tech%20conference%20this%20week%2C%20after%20explaining%20the%20startup's%20complex%20restructuring.%20%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20where%20we're%20going%2C%20think%20of%20OpenAI%20in%20terms%20of%20becoming%20very%20much%20a%20full%20stack%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20full%20stack%2C%20Friar%20means%20a%20tech%20company%20that%20owns%20and%20operates%20every%20part%20of%20its%20business.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20startup%20is%20already%20working%20on%20its%20own%20solutions%20for%20almost%20every%20ingredient%20needed%20for%20AI%20success.%20That%20includes%20designing%20its%20own%20chips%20and%20building%20its%20own%20data%20centers%2C%20all%20the%20way%20up%20the%20stack%20to%20a%20suite%20of%20AI-powered%20software%20applications%20beyond%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%2C%20as%20you%20look%20forward%2C%20will%20become%20very%20much%20a%20full%20stack%20company%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20places%20that%20we%20can%20build%20both%20moats%20and%20really%20interesting%20business%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Friar%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarah%20Friar%2C%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20speaks%20during%20the%20Reuters%20NEXT%20conference%2C%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20U.S.%2C%20December%2010%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c0949d32af4d666ef7944a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Friar%2C%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20of%20OpenAI%3Cp%3EMike%20Segar%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20say%20it%2C%20but%20the%20target%20is%20most%20likely%20Google.%20The%20search%20giant%20has%20spent%2025%20years%20developing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20blocks%20it%20needs%20to%20win%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20includes%20energy%20assets%2C%20specialized%20in-house%20chips%2C%20massive%20data%20centers%2C%20leading%20AI%20models%2C%20talent%2C%20developer%20platforms%2C%20wide%20distribution%2C%20and%20billions%20of%20consumer%20and%20enterprise%20touchpoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20a%20long%20way%20from%20Google's%20dominance%2C%20but%20the%20startup%20has%20several%20strategy%20beachheads%20from%20which%20to%20expand%20%E2%80%94%20both%20up%20and%20down%20the%20stack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb498143-a2e3-4b70-b0a9-e64aad2a8ab6%5C%22%3EEnergy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20AI%20tech%20stack%2C%20there's%20energy.%20GPUs%2C%20AI%20servers%2C%20and%20data%20centers%20consume%20unprecedented%20amounts%20of%20power.%20OpenAI%20doesn't%20have%20a%20clear%20answer%20here%20yet%3B%20however%2C%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20personally%20backed%20several%20energy%20startups%2C%20including%20Helion%2C%20which%20is%20trying%20to%20use%20nuclear%20fusion%20to%20generate%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f082bbf-caf9-47e8-b8bc-46ced8886591%5C%22%3EChips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20AI%20chips%20that%20are%20essential%20for%20training%20and%20running%20AI%20models.%20OpenAI%20hired%20Richard%20Ho%20in%20late%202023%20to%20lead%20its%20efforts%20here.%20He%20worked%20at%20Google%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20helping%20to%20develop%20the%20tech%20giant's%20TPUs%2C%20which%20power%20its%20AI%20models%2C%20including%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228eccc1fa-010f-4618-b7f8-a3d7bb86b7b4%5C%22%3EData%20centers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20AI%20chips%20go%20in%20servers%20that%20are%20stacked%20inside%20giant%20data%20centers.%20OpenAI%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20all%20the%20major%20cloud%20providers%2C%20renting%20the%20computing%20power%20needed%20to%20train%20and%20run%20its%20models%20and%20chatbot%20service.%20However%2C%20Friar%2C%20the%20CFO%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20OpenAI%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cfo-sarah-friar-cloud-giants-learning-on-our-dime-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20its%20own%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20rarely%20seen%20scaled%20technology%20companies%20that%20don't%20own%20and%20operate%20their%20own%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20Sachs%20internet%20analyst%20Eric%20Sheridan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BThis%20helps%20them%20control%20more%20of%20their%20own%20destinies%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfee23a6-49b4-45fa-b037-0b357703ace5%5C%22%3EModels%20and%20developers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20model%20layer%2C%20OpenAI%20has%20already%20established%20a%20beachhead%2C%20with%20a%20frontier%20offering%2C%20GPT-5%2C%20that%20is%20among%20the%20best.%20It%20also%20recently%20launched%20a%20powerful%20open-weight%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20APIs%20that%20developers%20use%20to%20tap%20into%20these%20models.%20About%204%20million%20developers%20have%20built%20on%20this%20OpenAI%20platform%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e048f1ae-4262-4db1-a6a7-c9f68d9f781c%5C%22%3EDistribution%20and%20gadgets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20broad%20distribution%2C%20no%20one%20will%20use%20your%20AI%20products.%20OpenAI%20is%20working%20on%20new%20ways%20to%20get%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20services%20to%20consumers.%20The%20startup%20bought%20Jony%20Ive's%20AI%20gadget%20startup%20for%20more%20than%20%246%20billion%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20and%20executives%20have%20hinted%20at%20form%20factors%20that%20could%20mean%20OpenAI's%20chatbot%20follows%20people%20wherever%20they%20go.%20It%20also%2