%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatthew-prince-search-engines-ai-cloudflare-google-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECloudflare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helps%20run%20about%2020%25%20of%20the%20world's%20websites%2C%20has%20begun%20tracking%20this%20behavior.%20It%20measures%20Big%20Tech%20company%20bots'%20requests%20to%20crawl%20websites%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20referrals%20the%20platforms%20send%20to%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20crawl-to-refer%20ratio%20is%20a%20useful%20guide%20to%20how%20much%20tech%20companies%20are%20taking%20from%20the%20web%20and%20how%20much%20they're%20giving%20back.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20ratio%20of%20100%20to%201%20would%20mean%20a%20company's%20bots%20crawled%20sites%20100%20times%20for%20every%201%20referral%20they%20send.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20one%20way%20to%20measure%20how%20ethical%20companies%20are%20in%20the%20AI%20era%3F%20I'll%20leave%20you%20to%20decide.%20Here's%20the%20data%20for%20the%20first%20week%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FAP1KX%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bar%20Chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FAP1KX%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-rewriting-startup-pay-levels-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20out%20like%20a%20sore%20thumb.%20According%20to%20Cloudflare%20data%2C%20it%20crawls%20sites%20way%20more%20than%20it%20sends%20users%20out%20to%20the%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20aligns%20with%20Business%20Insider%20reporting%20from%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%20Back%20then%2C%20we%20told%20you%20that%20bots%20from%20Anthropic%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-warns-agi-money-obsolete-while-raising-billions-usd-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%2C%20were%20crawling%20some%20websites%20so%20much%20that%20it%20was%20causing%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-ai-bots-havoc-raise-cloud-costs-websites-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraffic%20costs%20to%20spike%20dramatically%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20web%20developer%20saw%20a%20client's%C2%A0cloud-computing%20costs%20double%20within%20a%20few%20months%20due%C2%A0to%20this%20AI%20bot%20swarm%2C%20according%20to%20BI%20reporting%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20not%20only%20are%20AI%20companies%20taking%20from%20the%20web%20and%20giving%20less%20back%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20also%20leaving%20some%20site%20owners%20with%20bigger%20bills%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Anthropic%20why%20it%20crawls%20so%20much%20and%20gives%20so%20little%20back%20to%20the%20web.%20The%20startup%20said%20it%20couldn't%20confirm%20the%20crawl-to-refer%20ratios%20calculated%20by%20Cloudflare%20and%20said%20there%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Bissues%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20methodology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20also%20noted%20that%20it%20launched%20a%20web%20search%20feature%20for%20its%20popular%20Claude%20AI%20chatbot%20earlier%20this%20year.%20This%20is%20generating%20more%20referral%20traffic%20for%20websites%20now%2C%20and%20this%20is%20growing%20quickly%2C%20the%20startup%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Perplexity%20responded%20with%20a%20detailed%20and%20thoughtful%20response%20that%20partly%20focused%20on%20the%20emerging%20ability%20of%20bots%20to%20represent%20human%20users'%20intentions%2C%20such%20as%20a%20desire%20to%20access%20knowledge%20on%20the%20web%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20of%20public%20content%2C%20publishers%20can%20choose%20not%20to%20make%20their%20content%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Perplexity%20spokesperson%20Jesse%20Dwyer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20of%20facts%2C%20copyright%20law%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20has%20always%20drawn%20a%20line%20between%20facts%20and%20expression.%20That's%20a%20foundation%20of%20human%20inquiry%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20caveat%3A%20The%20numbers%20that%20go%20into%20the%20crawl-to-refer%20ratio%20focus%20on%20the%20web%20and%20exclude%20native%20app%20activity.%20If%20app%20activity%20were%20included%2C%20the%20ratios%20might%20be%20lower.%20However%2C%20this%20methodology%20applies%20to%20all%20the%20companies%20included%20in%20this%20ranking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E's%20relatively%20low%20ratio%20is%20likely%20due%20to%20its%20traditional%20search%20engine%2C%20which%20still%20shows%20website%20links%20in%20many%20results.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20is%20increasingly%20weaving%20in%20AI%20chatbot-style%20answers%20into%20its%20search%20service%2C%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-generative-experience-ai-lady-gaga-sge-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20Overviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20AI%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Cloudflare%20data%2C%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20January%2C%20Google's%20crawl-to-refer%20ratio%20was%203.3%20to%201.%20That%20ratio%20jumped%20to%2018%20to%201%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20April%20and%20then%20fell%20slightly%20to%209%20to%201%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20says%20it%20still%20sends%20traffic%20to%20the%20web%2C%20and%20it%20cares%20about%20the%20health%20of%20this%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20will%20track%20this%20Cloudflare%20data%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20quarters%20to%20see%20how%20this%20behavior%20evolve