t%3BThe%20Late%20Show%26quot%3B%20host%20said%20machines%20can't%20replicate%20the%20flaws%20that%20make%20art%20human.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Colbert%20doesn't%20buy%20that%20machines%20can%20make%20art%20that%20feels%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%26quot%3B%20host%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BPossible%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20Wednesday%20that%20AI%20can%20mimic%20art%20but%20will%20always%20struggle%20to%20escape%20the%20%26quot%3Buncanny%20valley.%26quot%3B%20He%20asked%20whether%20AI-generated%20art%20will%20ever%20stop%20feeling%20%26quot%3Balien.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20art%20comes%20from%20people%20because%20it%20fuses%20ideas%20with%20emotional%20experience%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArt%20is%20by%20humans%20for%20humans%20about%20being%20human.%20It's%20not%20about%20ideas%20because%20ideas%20are%20constructs%2C%20and%20humans%20are%20not%20a%20construct%2C%26quot%3B%20Colbert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20%26quot%3Bexperience%20ideas%20and%20they%20have%20emotional%20responses%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20art%2C%20Colbert%20also%20likened%20AI-mediated%20experiences%20to%20eating%20processed%20food%3A%20technically%20complete%2C%20but%20missing%20something%20vital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20growing%20suspicion%20that%20there%20are%20micronutrients%20of%20which%20we%20are%20not%20aware%20that%20we%20are%20robbed%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20%26quot%3Bmicronutrients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20may%20lie%20in%20the%20very%20failures%20and%20imperfections%20of%20human%20connection.%20The%20flawed%20nature%20of%20human%20interactions%20is%20inextricable%20from%20our%20experience%20of%20the%20world%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColbert%20isn't%20dismissing%20AI%20altogether.%20He%20said%20the%20technology%20could%20expand%20access%20to%20healthcare%20in%20underserved%20regions%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Ba%20medical%20station%20manned%20by%20AI%26quot%3B%20might%20be%20better%20than%20nothing.%20But%20he%20remains%20skeptical%20of%20claims%20that%20machines%20can%20replicate%20human%20intimacy%2C%20such%20as%20in%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColbert%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289ce3252-694f-4d26-aea5-7715f14bd415%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20and%20art%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20already%20begun%20reshaping%20the%20art%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hollywood%2C%20studio%20giants%20have%20spoken%20publicly%20about%20their%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20pitching%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-new-normal-spending-decline-peak-tv-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20make%20better%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELionsgate%20last%20September%20said%20it%20would%20work%20with%20Runway%20to%20experiment%20with%20its%20AI%20tools.%20AMC%20Networks%20followed%20suit%20this%20year.%20Amazon%20has%20talked%20about%20its%20use%20of%20AI%20to%20provide%20TV%20recaps%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffable-amazon-funding-showrunner-platform-pitch-deck-hollywood-studios-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvested%20in%20Fable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20lets%20people%20make%20their%20own%20TV%20shows%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20said%20in%20July%20that%20the%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20Eternaut%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20streamer's%20first%20to%20have%20shots%20fully%20generated%20by%20AI%20in%20its%20final%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20VFX%20sequence%20was%20completed%2010%20times%20faster%20than%20it%20could%20have%20been%20completed%20with%20visual%2C%20traditional%20VFX%20tools%20and%20workflows%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said%20about%20visual%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20OpenAI's%20new%20image%20generator%20sparked%20a%20tsunami%20of%20Studio%20Ghibli-style%20memes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-studio-ghibli-style-images-violate-copyright-or-not-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20copyright%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%20But%20OpenAI's%20CEO%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20said%20in%20April%20that%20AI%20art%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bnet%20win%26quot%3B%20for%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20in%20an%C2%A0interview%C2%A0published%20on%20YouTube%20by%20the%20founder%20and%20content%20creator%20Varun%20Mayya%20that%20AI%20can%20expand%20creativity%20by%20lowering%20the%20barriers%20to%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20many%20worry%20about%20unauthorized%20or%20ethically%20questionable%20uses%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Disney%20and%20NBCUniversal%20sued%20the%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-universal-midjourney-images-evidence-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompany%20Midjourney%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20it%20stole%20their%20famous%20characters%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Simpsons%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMinions.%26quot%3B%20Midjourney%20denied%20the%20claims%20in%20its%20legal%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20central%20to%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20says%20Amazon%20MGM%20Studios%20violated%20copyright%20in%20its%20%26quot%3BRoad%20House%26quot%3B%20remake%20and%20used%20AI%20to%20replicate%20actors'%20voices%20to%20finish%20the%20film%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20labor%20contracts.%20Amazon%20said%20the%20suit%20was%20without%20merit%20and%20that%20the%20film%20didn't%20use%20AI-cloned%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstephen-colbert-hangup-ai-created-art-uncanny-valley-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17576