-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-223x300.jpg%20223w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-768x1033.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1142x1536.jpg%201142w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1523x2048.jpg%201523w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1200x1614.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-150x202.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescue%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%20when%20Menon%20and%20his%20team%20started%20the%20rescue%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20orphan%20elephant%20calves%20to%20reintroduce%20them%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20people%20discouraged%20the%20idea.%20But%20the%20conservationist%